	* README
	  README.jp: added the "How to run" section.

2001-05-19

	* merged NNTP AUTH from the claws branch.
	* src/news.[ch]: supported NNTP AUTH.
	* src/nntp.[ch]: wrapped SockInfo with NNTPSockInfo for NNTP AUTH.
	* INSTALL
