	* src/folderview.c: modified so that it uses gtkut_wait_for_draw()
	  instead of GTK_EVENTS_FLUSH() for statusbar redraw.
	* src/codeconv.[ch]
	  src/mainwindow.c
	  src/prefs_common.c: added Baltic (ISO-8859-4,13) to the code sets.
