	* src/textview.[ch]: implemented clickable URI (thanks to BONAIM).
	  And made `X-Mailer:' header emphasized if it contains `Sylpheed'.

2000-05-04

	* src/summaryview.c: summary_write_cache(): permission fix of
	  cache file.

